{"data":[{"date":"18:57 14/08","title":"Ronaldo \u0111\u1ebfn Juventus khi\u1ebfn Serie A \u201cl\u00ean h\u01b0\u01a1ng\u201d","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Italia","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/31/matthaus-phat-bieu-ve-viec-ronaldo-den-juventus.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Lothar Matthaus ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c Ronaldo \u0111\u1ebfn Juventus. Huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c tin r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u00e2y s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u00fa h\u00edch l\u1edbn \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u Serie A \u0111\u00e3 ng\u1ee5p l\u1eb7n nhi\u1ec1u n\u0103m qua.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 \u201cbom t\u1ea5n\u201d Ronaldo</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNgay sau khi gi\u00e0nh ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Champions League c\u00f9ng Real Madrid m\u00f9a 2017/18, Cristiano Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 b\u00f3ng gi\u00f3 v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c s\u1ebd ra \u0111i. Kh\u00f4ng l\u00e2u sau, anh gia nh\u1eadp Juventus theo b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 112 tri\u1ec7u euro.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Real, Ronaldo ghi t\u1edbi 450 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng sau 438 tr\u1eadn. Anh c\u00f9ng Los Blancos gi\u00e0nh 4 chi\u1ebfc c\u00fap Champions League v\u00e0 \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 trong v\u00f2ng 5 n\u0103m qua. <br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Lothar Matthaus ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c Ronaldo \u0111\u1ebfn Juventus h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Lothar Matthaus ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c Ronaldo \u0111\u1ebfn Juventus h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/31/matthaus-phat-bieu-ve-viec-ronaldo-den-juventus.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Matthaus ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c Ronaldo \u0111\u1ebfn Juventus t\u00edch c\u1ef1c</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u00f3 Ronaldo, Juventus hy v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ed5i \u0111\u1eddi t\u1ea1i Champions League. 22 n\u0103m qua, \u201cB\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea7m gi\u00e0\u201d ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n ch\u1ea1m tay v\u00e0o c\u00fap b\u1ea1c ch\u00e2u \u00c2u b\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5p \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ed1ng tr\u1ecb Serie A 7 n\u0103m li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp.</div>\r\n<h2><br>\r\nMatthaus tin Ronaldo l\u00e0 c\u00fa h\u00edch</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nLothar Matthaus, c\u1ef1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a Inter Milan (1988 t\u1edbi 1992) d\u00e0nh nhi\u1ec1u k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng v\u00e0o Cristiano Ronaldo. Matthaus ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c Ronaldo \u0111\u1ebfn Juventus v\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u suy ngh\u0129 l\u1ea1c quan v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y v\u00e0 c\u1ea3 Serie A.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cV\u1ee5 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng n\u00e0y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n cho c\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 v\u00e0 c\u00e1c b\u1ed9 ph\u1eadn ti\u1ebfp th\u1ecb\u201d, c\u1ef1u tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 \u0110\u1ee9c n\u00f3i v\u1edbi t\u1edd Bild. \u201cNh\u1eefng hi\u1ec7u \u1ee9ng xung quanh Ronaldo l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn. Serie A r\u1ea5t c\u00f3 l\u1ee3i t\u1eeb s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i n\u00e0y. Ronaldo kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n \u1edf \u0111\u1ed9 ch\u00edn c\u1ee7a s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p. T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1ebd t\u1eadp trung v\u00e0o Champions League.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u00f9a n\u00e0y, Matthaus tin t\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u0169 Inter Milan s\u1ebd l\u00e0m n\u00ean chuy\u1ec7n. \u0110o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Luciano Spalletti \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u s\u1ef1 b\u1ed5 sung ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 n\u00e0y v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n s\u1ebd c\u00f9ng Juventus c\u1ea1nh tranh Scudetto.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cInter \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 n\u1eeda sau m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi v\u00e0 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u00e9 d\u1ef1 Champions League\u201d, Matthaus n\u00f3i th\u00eam. \u201ch\u1ecd c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 gi\u1ecfi trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh. Inter \u0111ang th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n s\u1ef1 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh, g\u1ecdn g\u00e0ng v\u00e0 m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 Cristiano Ronaldo tr\u00ean trang bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/ronaldo-muon-juventus-mua-muc-tieu-so-1-cua-mu-o-he-2018-176-194317.html\">Ronaldo mu\u1ed1n Juventus mua m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau s\u1ed1 1 c\u1ee7a MU</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/ronaldo-thuc-giuc-nguoi-ban-than-marcelo-den-juventus-176-194109.html\">Ronaldo th\u00fac gi\u1ee5c ng\u01b0\u1eddi b\u1ea1n th\u00e2n \u0111\u1ebfn Juventus</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/ronaldo-co-the-dua-juve-den-tam-cao-moi-176-194082.html\">Ronaldo c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a Juve \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1ea7m cao m\u1edbi</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/co-cristiano-ronaldo-serie-a-doi-logo-176-194058.html\">C\u00f3 Cristiano Ronaldo, Serie A CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C \u0111\u1ed5i sang logo m\u1edbi</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5498","checkdouble":"194487"},{"date":"06:46 15/08","title":"CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C: AS Roma chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Italia","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/15/chinh-thuc-as-roma-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-nha-vo-dich-world-cup.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>D\u01b0\u1edbi t\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u1ee7a Monchi, AS Roma chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Steven Nzonzi, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 v\u1eeba v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018 c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Ph\u00e1p.</h2><h2>AS Roma chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Steven Nzonzi<br>\r\n\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trang ch\u1ee7 AS Roma m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u01b0a ra th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Steven Nzonzi t\u1eeb Sevilla v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 26.65 tri\u1ec7u euro. B\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 29 tu\u1ed5i v\u1edbi Giallorossi c\u00f3 th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n 4 n\u0103m, k\u00e8m \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n ph\u00ed b\u1ed5 sung 4 tri\u1ec7u euro t\u00f9y v\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y trong th\u1eddi gian kho\u00e1c \u00e1o \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Rome.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C AS Roma chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Steven Nzonzi h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C AS Roma chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Steven Nzonzi h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/15/chinh-thuc-as-roma-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-nha-vo-dich-world-cup.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>AS Roma chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Steven Nzonzi.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 mang \u0111\u1eadm \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng t\u1eeb gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Monchi, b\u1edfi Nzonzi nguy\u00ean l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a Sevilla - \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u0169 n\u01a1i G\u0110 Monchi t\u1eebng l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c. Nzonzi t\u1eebng c\u00f3 ba m\u00f9a thi \u0111\u1ea5u cho Sevilla tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi t\u1edbi AS Roma nh\u1eadn chi\u1ebfc \u00e1o s\u1ed1 42.\u00a0<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nzonzi g\u00e2y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng khi g\u00f3p c\u00f4ng l\u1edbn gi\u00fap \u0110T Ph\u00e1p v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018. Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 ra s\u00e2n 5 trong s\u1ed1 7 tr\u1eadn c\u1ee7a Les Bleus t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u. T\u00ednh \u0111\u1ebfn nay, Nzonzi \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 t\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng 9 l\u1ea7n kho\u00e1c \u00e1o \u0110TQG.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi trong cu\u1ed9c n\u00f3i g\u00ec<br>\r\n\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau khi gia nh\u1eadp AS Roma, Nzonzi cho bi\u1ebft: \"T\u00f4i c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac \u1edf \u0111\u00e2y khi tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 m\u1edbi c\u1ee7a Roma. T\u00f4i lu\u00f4n mu\u1ed1n ti\u1ebfn b\u1ed9 h\u01a1n n\u1eefa, b\u1ea5t k\u1ec3 tu\u1ed5i t\u00e1c, \u0111i\u1ec1u quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 l\u00e0m \u0111i\u1ec1u t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t v\u00e0 th\u1eadt n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n l\u00e0m \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n, gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ee1 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng b\u1eb1ng c\u00e1ch ch\u01a1i v\u00e0 kinh nghi\u1ec7m b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n\".<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 t\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u1ee7a b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n trong vi\u1ec7c AS Roma chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Steven Nzonzi, G\u0110 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Monchi cho bi\u1ebft: \"Nzonzi l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 pha tr\u1ed9n gi\u1eefa m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd v\u1ec1 th\u1ec3 ch\u1ea5t v\u00e0 ph\u1ea9m ch\u1ea5t k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 l\u00fd do ch\u00fang t\u00f4i th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 mu\u1ed1n chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y\".<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\"V\u1edbi s\u1ef1 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Nzonzi, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1edf h\u1eefu tuy\u1ebfn ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 gi\u00e0u ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0 t\u00ednh c\u1ea1nh tranh cao h\u01a1n\".<br>\r\n<h2>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn v\u1ec1 AS Roma m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018-19:</h2>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/roma-chuan-bi-bao-thu-barca-thanh-cong-180-194430.html\">Roma chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb \u201cb\u00e1o th\u00f9\u201d Barca th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/hau-truong/chu-tich-roma-treo-thuong-bang-sieu-xe-lamborghini-188-194092.html\">Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Roma treo th\u01b0\u1edfng b\u1eb1ng si\u00eau xe Lamborghini</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/real-madrid-vs-roma-tran-dau-icc-2018-372-193968.html\">Real Madrid 2-1 Roma (KT): Bale t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng, Los Blancos th\u1eafng tr\u1eadn cu\u1ed1i \u1edf ICC 2018</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/roma-bat-ngo-muon-rut-ruot-arsenal-172-193727.html\">Roma b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd mu\u1ed1n r\u00fat ru\u1ed9t Arsenal</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/muc-tieu-so-1-cua-arsenal-dat-duoc-thoa-thuan-voi-roma-172-192633.html\">M\u1ee5c ti\u00eau s\u1ed1 1 c\u1ee7a Arsenal \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn v\u1edbi Roma</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/muc-tieu-cua-chelsea-dong-y-o-lai-serie-a-176-192603.html\">M\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a Chelsea \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd \u1edf l\u1ea1i Serie A</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>N.D (TTVN)</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5497","checkdouble":"194508"},{"date":"21:06 14/08","title":"V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft n\u00f3i \u0111\u1ee1 cho C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng sau m\u00e0n \u0111\u00e1 penalty th\u1ea3m h\u1ecda","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/14/van-quyet-noi-do-cho-cong-phuong-sau-man-da-tham-hoa.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Nguy\u1ec5n V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft cho bi\u1ebft m\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e3 nh\u01b0\u1eddng quy\u1ec1n s\u00fat 11m cho \u2018\u0111\u00e0n em\u2019 C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00ec m\u1ed9t l\u00fd do.</h2><h2>V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft n\u00f3i \u0111\u1ee1 cho C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng sau m\u00e0n \u0111\u00e1 penalty th\u1ea3m h\u1ecda</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n t\u1ea1i m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam ASIAD 2018, \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng g\u1eb7p nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Pakistan v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t 3-0.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y, b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh nh\u1eefng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng m\u00e0 c\u00e1c ch\u00e0ng trai \u00e1o \u0111\u1ecf ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c, ng\u01b0\u1eddi ta c\u0169ng ch\u00fa \u00fd nhi\u1ec1u t\u1edbi hai l\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e1 h\u1ecfng penalty c\u1ee7a C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng khi anh kh\u00f4ng s\u00fat tr\u00fang x\u00e0 ngang d\u1ed9i ra th\u00ec c\u0169ng b\u1ecb th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ea3n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft n\u00f3i \u0111\u1ee1 cho C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng sau m\u00e0n \u0111\u00e1 penalty th\u1ea3m h\u1ecda h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft n\u00f3i \u0111\u1ee1 cho C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng sau m\u00e0n \u0111\u00e1 penalty th\u1ea3m h\u1ecda h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/14/van-quyet-noi-do-cho-cong-phuong-sau-man-da-tham-hoa.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>\u00a0C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n kh\u00f4ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng 2 qu\u1ea3 penalty \u1edf tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Paksitan</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u00f3i v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec7n n\u00e0y, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 vi\u1ec7c m\u00ecnh nh\u01b0\u1eddng 2 qu\u1ea3 ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n cho C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00ec c\u1ea3m nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c r\u00f5 khao kh\u00e1t ghi b\u00e0n t\u1edbi t\u1eeb ng\u00f4i sao x\u1ee9 Ngh\u1ec7.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u1ee7 qu\u00e2n Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam chia s\u1ebb: \u201cT\u00f4i lu\u00f4n \u0111\u1eb7t t\u1eadp th\u1ec3 l\u00ean \u0111\u1ea7u. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ai c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n ghi b\u00e0n, nh\u01b0ng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i lu\u00f4n t\u1ea1o \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n tr\u00ean h\u1ebft cho nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 kh\u00e1t khao. H\u00f4m nay, Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u00f3 \u00e1p l\u1ef1c nh\u01b0ng r\u1ea5t kh\u00e1t khao. To\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y. D\u00f9 c\u00f3 ghi b\u00e0n hay kh\u00f4ng, to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i v\u1eabn lu\u00f4n \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1u th\u1ea5y \u0111\u1ea5y. Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng kh\u00f4ng ghi b\u00e0n nh\u01b0ng sau \u0111\u1ea5y n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng. B\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u0169ng l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac cho to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i v\u00ec ch\u00fang t\u00f4i t\u1ea1o ni\u1ec1m tin cho c\u1eadu \u1ea5y\u201d.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft c\u0169ng cho bi\u1ebft sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng 3-0 \u1edf ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n, tinh th\u1ea7n c\u1ee7a to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111ang r\u1ea5t tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i v\u00e0 vui v\u1ebb. M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o n\u00e0y kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd nhanh ch\u00f3ng qu\u00ean \u0111i ni\u1ec1m vui n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Nepal trong 2 ng\u00e0y n\u1eefa.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/thay-gi-sau-tran-olympic-viet-nam-30-olympic-pakistan-168-194498.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/14/thay-gi-sau-tran-olympic-viet-nam-30-olympic-pakistan.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/thay-gi-sau-tran-olympic-viet-nam-30-olympic-pakistan-168-194498.html\">Th\u1ea5y g\u00ec sau tr\u1eadn Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam 3-0 Olympic Pakistan?</span><br>\r\n\u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u di\u1ec5n ra chi\u1ec1u 14/8, \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng kh\u00f4ng m\u1ea5y kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Olympic Pakistan. V\u00e0 d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n \u1edf...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-park-hang-seo-van-chua-hai-long-du-thang-pakistan-168-194496.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/14/hlv-park-hang-seo-van-chua-hai-long-du-thang-pakistan.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-park-hang-seo-van-chua-hai-long-du-thang-pakistan-168-194496.html\">HLV Park Hang Seo v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng d\u00f9 th\u1eafng Pakistan</span><br>\r\nSau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, HLV Park Hang Seo \u0111\u00e3 cho bi\u1ebft \u00f4ng kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1ec1 m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 d\u00f9 Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 3-0.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-pakistan-noi-gi-sau-tran-thua-olympic-viet-nam-168-194488.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/14/hlv-pakistan-noi-gi-sau-tran-thua-olympic-viet-nam.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-pakistan-noi-gi-sau-tran-thua-olympic-viet-nam-168-194488.html\">HLV Pakistan n\u00f3i g\u00ec sau tr\u1eadn thua Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam?</span><br>\r\nPh\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u trong bu\u1ed5i h\u1ecdp b\u00e1o sau tr\u1eadn, \u00f4ng Jose Antonio Noguira, HLV \u0110T Olympic Pakistan \u0111\u00e3 d\u00e0nh nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi khen ng\u1ee3i cho l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Olympic Vi\u1ec7t...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/clip-olympic-viet-nam-vs-olympic-pakistan-30-325-194482.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/14/clip-olympic-viet-nam-vs-olympic-pakistan-30.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/video/clip-olympic-viet-nam-vs-olympic-pakistan-30-325-194482.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam 3-0 Olympic Pakistan (Asiad 2018)</span><br>\r\nTh\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Park Hang Seo \u0111\u00e3 kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam ASIAD 2018 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng khi th\u1eafng thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c Olympic Pakistan. L\u1ebd ra, ch\u00fang ta c\u00f2n th\u1eafng \u0111\u1eadm h\u01a1n n\u1eefa n\u1ebfu...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:\n115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5496","checkdouble":"194499"},{"date":"21:25 14/08","title":"Sergio Aguero c\u0169ng t\u1eebng hai l\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e1 h\u1ecfng 11m trong m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u nh\u01b0 C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/14/sergio-aguero-cung-tung-hai-lan-da-hong-11m-trong-mot-tran-dau-nhu-cong-phuong.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>C\u00f3 l\u1ebd nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi v\u1eabn cho r\u1eb1ng ph\u1ea3i r\u1ea5t t\u1ec7 m\u1edbi c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n h\u1ecfng c\u1ea3 hai qu\u1ea3 11m trong m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u nh\u01b0 C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng, song tr\u00ean th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi v\u1eabn c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf.</h2><h2>Sergio Aguero c\u0169ng t\u1eebng hai l\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e1 h\u1ecfng 11m nh\u01b0 C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng <o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Sergio Aguero c\u0169ng t\u1eebng hai l\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e1 h\u1ecfng 11m nh\u01b0 C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Sergio Aguero c\u0169ng t\u1eebng hai l\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e1 h\u1ecfng 11m nh\u01b0 C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/14/374E6C73000005783745091imagea41_1471435666380.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Sergio Aguero c\u0169ng t\u1eebng \u0111\u00e1 h\u1ecfng 2 qu\u1ea3 penalty trong m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u nh\u01b0 C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u00e0 Pakistan chi\u1ec1u ng\u00e0y 14/8, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t 3-0.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y, b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh nh\u1eefng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng m\u00e0 Quang H\u1ea3i, V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft v\u00e0 C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c, ng\u01b0\u1eddi ta c\u0169ng ch\u00fa \u00fd nhi\u1ec1u t\u1edbi hai l\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e1 h\u1ecfng penalty c\u1ee7a C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng khi anh n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng s\u00fat tr\u00fang x\u00e0 ngang d\u1ed9i ra th\u00ec c\u0169ng b\u1ecb th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ea3n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00e1 h\u1ecfng c\u1ea3 2 qu\u1ea3 11m trong m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, \u0111\u00e2y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 xem l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t th\u1ea3m h\u1ecda s\u00fat 11m. Song tr\u00ean th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi kh\u00f4ng hi\u1ebfm nh\u1eefng tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p nh\u01b0 v\u1eady.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng 5-0 c\u1ee7a CLB Man City tr\u01b0\u1edbc Steaua Bucharest t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng play-off UEFA Champions League m\u00f9a 2016/17, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Sergio Aguero c\u0169ng m\u1eafc ph\u1ea3i sai l\u1ea7m y chang C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng. M\u0169i nh\u1ecdn c\u1ee7a Man City \u0111\u00e1 h\u1ecfng 2 qu\u1ea3 11 m trong tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y, tuy nhi\u00ean b\u00f9 l\u1ea1i Aguero \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m kh\u00e1 t\u1ed1t nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 ghi b\u00e0n v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c ghi m\u1ed9t c\u00fa hat-trick b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00fap Man xanh \u0111\u00e8 b\u1eb9p \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n Romania v\u1edbi t\u1ed5ng t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 6-0.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ngo\u00e0i Aguero, m\u1ed9t ng\u00f4i sao kh\u00e1c c\u0169ng t\u1eebng \u0111\u00e1 h\u1ecfng 2 qu\u1ea3 11m trong 1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u l\u00e0 c\u1ef1u sao Chelsea, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Oscar. \u0110\u00f3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao Brazil khi anh \u0111\u00e1 h\u1ecfng c\u1ea3 2 qu\u1ea3 11m, qua \u0111\u00f3 khi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 th\u1ea5t th\u1ee7 v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 0-1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc CLB \u00a0Urawa Reds \u1edf gi\u1ea3i AFC Champions League m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ngo\u00e0i hai c\u00e1i t\u00ean \u0111\u00e3 n\u00eau, m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 ng\u00f4i sao ti\u1ebfng t\u0103m kh\u00e1c nh\u01b0 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Saido Berahino c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e1 h\u1ecfng 2 qu\u1ea3 penalty trong tr\u1eadn West Brom g\u1eb7p Watford \u1edf gi\u1ea3i ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh m\u00f9a b\u00f3ng 2015/16 hay ch\u00e2n s\u00fat Darren Bent b\u1ecf ph\u00ed 2 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i th\u00e0nh b\u00e0n c\u1ee7a Sunderland tr\u01b0\u1edbc Tottenham trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 4/2010.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9 t\u1eebng ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1 h\u1ecfng t\u1edbi 3 qu\u1ea3 ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n trong c\u00f9ng 1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p c\u1ee7a c\u1ef1u danh th\u1ee7 Martin Palermo \u1edf tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Colombia t\u1ea1i Coppa America 1999. T\u1eebng n\u1ed5i l\u00ean nh\u01b0 truy\u1ec1n nh\u00e2n x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng nh\u1ea5t cho huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Batistuta, tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh s\u1eadp ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a Martin Palermo v\u00e0 khi\u1ebfn anh kh\u00f4ng bao gi\u1edd v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u1eefa.\u00a0</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/thay-gi-sau-tran-olympic-viet-nam-30-olympic-pakistan-168-194498.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/14/thay-gi-sau-tran-olympic-viet-nam-30-olympic-pakistan.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/thay-gi-sau-tran-olympic-viet-nam-30-olympic-pakistan-168-194498.html\">Th\u1ea5y g\u00ec sau tr\u1eadn Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam 3-0 Olympic Pakistan?</span><br>\r\n\u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u di\u1ec5n ra chi\u1ec1u 14/8, \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng kh\u00f4ng m\u1ea5y kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Olympic Pakistan. V\u00e0 d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n \u1edf...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/van-quyet-noi-do-cho-cong-phuong-sau-man-da-tham-hoa-168-194499.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/14/van-quyet-noi-do-cho-cong-phuong-sau-man-da-tham-hoa.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/van-quyet-noi-do-cho-cong-phuong-sau-man-da-tham-hoa-168-194499.html\">V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft n\u00f3i \u0111\u1ee1 cho C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng sau m\u00e0n \u0111\u00e1 penalty th\u1ea3m h\u1ecda</span><br>\r\nChia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Nguy\u1ec5n V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft cho bi\u1ebft m\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e3 nh\u01b0\u1eddng quy\u1ec1n s\u00fat 11m cho \u2018\u0111\u00e0n em\u2019 C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00ec m\u1ed9t l\u00fd do.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-park-hang-seo-van-chua-hai-long-du-thang-pakistan-168-194496.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/14/hlv-park-hang-seo-van-chua-hai-long-du-thang-pakistan.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-park-hang-seo-van-chua-hai-long-du-thang-pakistan-168-194496.html\">HLV Park Hang Seo v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng d\u00f9 th\u1eafng Pakistan</span><br>\r\nSau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, HLV Park Hang Seo \u0111\u00e3 cho bi\u1ebft \u00f4ng kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1ec1 m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 d\u00f9 Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 3-0.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/clip-olympic-viet-nam-vs-olympic-pakistan-30-325-194482.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/14/clip-olympic-viet-nam-vs-olympic-pakistan-30.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/video/clip-olympic-viet-nam-vs-olympic-pakistan-30-325-194482.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam 3-0 Olympic Pakistan (Asiad 2018)</span><br>\r\nTh\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Park Hang Seo \u0111\u00e3 kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam ASIAD 2018 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng khi th\u1eafng thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c Olympic Pakistan. L\u1ebd ra, ch\u00fang ta c\u00f2n th\u1eafng \u0111\u1eadm h\u01a1n n\u1eefa n\u1ebfu...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 115%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5495","checkdouble":"194500"},{"date":"22:40 14/08","title":"C\u00e1c chuy\u00ean gia n\u00f3i g\u00ec khi C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng hai l\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e1 h\u1ecfng ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/14/congphuongdl_ynhd.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn vi\u1ec7c ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng hai l\u1ea7n th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n kh\u00f4ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u00e1c qu\u1ea3 \u0111\u00e1 11m, c\u1ea3 chuy\u00ean gia b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Tr\u1ecbnh Minh Hu\u1ebf l\u1eabn BLV Quang Huy \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a ra quan \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.\r\n\r\n\r\n</h2><h2>Chuy\u00ean gia n\u00f3i g\u00ec khi C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng hai l\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e1 h\u1ecfng ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n?</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Park Hang Seo tin t\u01b0\u1edfng cho \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh ngay t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i nh\u1eefng d\u1ea5u \u1ea5n \u0111\u1eadm n\u00e9t khi c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 t\u1ef1 m\u00ecnh ghi b\u00e0n \u1ea5n \u0111\u1ecbnh th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i 3-0 cho \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Pakistan.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 s\u1ebd ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o h\u01a1n v\u1edbi C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng trong l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u tham d\u1ef1 ASIAD n\u1ebfu anh kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1 h\u1ecfng 2 qu\u1ea3 ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n do ch\u00ednh anh v\u00e0 Quang H\u1ea3i ki\u1ebfm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><em><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chuy\u00ean gia n\u00f3i g\u00ec khi C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng hai l\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e1 h\u1ecfng ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Chuy\u00ean gia n\u00f3i g\u00ec khi C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng hai l\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e1 h\u1ecfng ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/14/congphuongdl_ynhd.jpg\"></em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng hai l\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e1 h\u1ecfng ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u00e0 Pakistan</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u00f3i v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c ng\u00f4i sao HAGL s\u00fat h\u1ecfng ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n, chuy\u00ean gia Tr\u1ecbnh Minh Hu\u1ebf n\u00f3i tr\u00ean VTC News: \"Nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n s\u00fat h\u1ecfng ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n c\u1ee7a C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t t\u1eeb t\u00e2m l\u00fd. C\u00f3 nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 m\u1edbi 17, 18 tu\u1ed5i m\u00e0 m\u1eb7t \u0111\u00e3 r\u1ea5t l\u1ef3, nh\u01b0 Kylian Mbappe l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t v\u00ed d\u1ee5, nh\u01b0ng c\u0169ng c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e1 b\u00f3ng m\u00e3i v\u1eabn c\u1ee9 b\u1ecb t\u00e2m l\u00fd.</p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">H\u1ec7 th\u1ea7n kinh m\u1ed7i ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u0169ng c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m kh\u00e1c nhau. Nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 k\u1ef9 - chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t, song c\u1ee9 ra s\u00e2n ho\u1eb7c g\u1eb7p kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n l\u00e0 c\u0103ng th\u1eb3ng c\u1ef1c \u0111\u1ed9. Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i b\u00e0n c\u00e3i, v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 ch\u1ec9 n\u1eb1m \u1edf t\u00e2m l\u00fd th\u00f4i\".</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u00ecnh lu\u1eadn v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec7n n\u00e0y, Gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c \u0111i\u1ec1u h\u00e0nh CLB SLNA H\u1ed3 V\u0103n Chi\u00eam l\u1ea1i chia s\u1ebb: \u201cT\u00f4i l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng th\u00edch c\u00e1i c\u00e1ch \u00f4ng \u00fd (HLV Park Hang Seo) cho Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n. \u1eea, th\u00ec c\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1eabn \u0111\u00e1 tinh t\u1ebf l\u1eafm. Nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n, n\u00ean b\u1ed1 tr\u00ed ng\u01b0\u1eddi kh\u00e1c. Thi\u1ebfu g\u00ec ng\u01b0\u1eddi. \u201cN\u00f3\u201d - l\u00e0 th\u1eb1ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u1ea5y s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t kh\u1ed5 n\u1ebfu \u0111\u00e1 h\u1ecfng. \u0110\u1eb1ng n\u00e0y l\u1ea1i c\u00f2n h\u1ecfng nh\u1eefng hai l\u1ea7n. Kh\u1ed5 n\u00f3 qu\u00e1, kh\u1ed5 n\u00f3 qu\u00e1\u201d.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, BHL Quang Huy l\u1ea1i nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng kh\u00f4ng g\u1eb7p nhi\u1ec1u s\u1ee9c \u00e9p khi hai l\u1ea7n s\u00fat h\u1ecfng penalty v\u00e0 s\u1ebd tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ti\u1ebfp theo.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u201c\u1ede ch\u1ea5m 11 m, b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 si\u00eau sao n\u00e0o tr\u00ean th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi c\u0169ng t\u1eebng s\u00fat h\u1ecfng ch\u1ee9 kh\u00f4ng ri\u00eang g\u00ec C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng. Diego Maradona, Michel Platini \u0111\u00e3 r\u01a1i v\u00e0o c\u1ea3nh nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf. V\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 l\u00e0 C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ea7n t\u1ef1 tin h\u01a1n cho c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i sau, c\u00f2n v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u1ee7a anh \u1edf \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam kh\u00f4ng b\u1ecb \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng. \u00d4ng Park r\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ec1 cao c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 kinh nghi\u1ec7m, do \u0111\u00f3 vai tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1eabn r\u1ea5t quan tr\u1ecdng\u201d, BHL Quang Huy cho bi\u1ebft.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i 3-0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Pakistan, Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111ang t\u1ea1m d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng D v\u1edbi 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u00f9ng hi\u1ec7u s\u1ed1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng/b\u1ea1i l\u00e0 +3, \u0111\u1ee9ng th\u1ee9 hai l\u00e0 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n sau th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i 1-0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Nepal. Hai \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec3m.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn ti\u1ebfp theo v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y 16/8, Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u Nepal l\u00fac 19h00, tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n v\u00e0 Pakistan l\u00fac 16h00.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/sergio-aguero-cung-tung-hai-lan-da-hong-11m-trong-mot-tran-dau-nhu-cong-phuong-168-194500.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/14/sergio-aguero-cung-tung-hai-lan-da-hong-11m-trong-mot-tran-dau-nhu-cong-phuong.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/sergio-aguero-cung-tung-hai-lan-da-hong-11m-trong-mot-tran-dau-nhu-cong-phuong-168-194500.html\">Sergio Aguero c\u0169ng t\u1eebng hai l\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e1 h\u1ecfng 11m trong m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u nh\u01b0 C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng</span><br>\r\nC\u00f3 l\u1ebd nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi v\u1eabn cho r\u1eb1ng ph\u1ea3i r\u1ea5t t\u1ec7 m\u1edbi c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n h\u1ecfng c\u1ea3 hai qu\u1ea3 11m trong m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u nh\u01b0 C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng, song tr\u00ean th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi v\u1eabn c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u tr\u01b0\u1eddng...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/van-quyet-noi-do-cho-cong-phuong-sau-man-da-tham-hoa-168-194499.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/14/van-quyet-noi-do-cho-cong-phuong-sau-man-da-tham-hoa.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/van-quyet-noi-do-cho-cong-phuong-sau-man-da-tham-hoa-168-194499.html\">V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft n\u00f3i \u0111\u1ee1 cho C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng sau m\u00e0n \u0111\u00e1 penalty th\u1ea3m h\u1ecda</span><br>\r\nChia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Nguy\u1ec5n V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft cho bi\u1ebft m\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e3 nh\u01b0\u1eddng quy\u1ec1n s\u00fat 11m cho \u2018\u0111\u00e0n em\u2019 C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00ec m\u1ed9t l\u00fd do.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/thay-gi-sau-tran-olympic-viet-nam-30-olympic-pakistan-168-194498.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/14/thay-gi-sau-tran-olympic-viet-nam-30-olympic-pakistan.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/thay-gi-sau-tran-olympic-viet-nam-30-olympic-pakistan-168-194498.html\">Th\u1ea5y g\u00ec sau tr\u1eadn Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam 3-0 Olympic Pakistan?</span><br>\r\n\u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u di\u1ec5n ra chi\u1ec1u 14/8, \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng kh\u00f4ng m\u1ea5y kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Olympic Pakistan. V\u00e0 d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n \u1edf...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)</p>\r\n<h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</p>\r\n</h2>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16.5pt;font-family:\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5494","checkdouble":"194501"},{"date":"23:00 14/08","title":"C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e1 11m d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi HLV Park Hang Seo?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/14/cong-phuong-khong-con-co-hoi-da-11m-duoi-thoi-hlv-park-hang-seo.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chia s\u1ebb c\u1ee7a HLV Park Hang Seo trong bu\u1ed5i h\u1ecdp b\u00e1o sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u cho th\u1ea5y nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n ni\u1ec1m tin v\u1edbi ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u01b0ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u1eefng qu\u1ea3 \u0111\u00e1 11m.</h2><h2>C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e1 11m sau tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Pakistan?</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u s\u1edbm t\u1ea1i b\u1ea3ng D, m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam ASIAD 2018, \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng g\u1eb7p nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Pakistan v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 3-0 sau c\u00e1c b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Quang H\u1ea3i, V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft v\u00e0 C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u BXH b\u1edfi \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u sau \u0111\u00f3, Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i 1-0 t\u1ed1i thi\u1ec3u tr\u01b0\u1edbc Nepal.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e1 11m d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi HLV Park Hang Seo h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e1 11m d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi HLV Park Hang Seo h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/14/photo1534244610614-1534244610614227491263.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1 penalty\u00a0d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi HLV Park Hang Seo?</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady, sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c v\u1eabn kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1ec1 m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00d4ng n\u00f3i: \u201cT\u00f4i h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1ec1 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean n\u00ean vi\u1ec7c c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 nh\u01b0 V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft, C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng, Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u01a1i ch\u01b0a \u0111\u00fang phong \u0111\u1ed9 l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 \u0111\u00e1ng lo ng\u1ea1i. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1ec1 ph\u1ea7n C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng, t\u1eeb b\u00e2y gi\u1edd, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn \u0111\u00e1 11m n\u1eefa\".<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chia s\u1ebb c\u1ee7a HLV Park Hang Seo cho th\u1ea5y C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n c\u00e1c qu\u1ea3 \u0111\u00e1 11m cho Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nN\u00ean nh\u1edb r\u1eb1ng, t\u1ea1i VCK U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1, ch\u00e2n s\u00fat x\u1ee9 Ngh\u1ec7 c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n m\u1ed9t c\u00fa s\u00fat n\u00e0o trong lo\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ea5u s\u00fang c\u00e2n n\u00e3o ph\u00e2n \u0111\u1ecbnh th\u1eafng b\u1ea1i t\u1ea1i t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft g\u1eb7p Iraq, c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 \u1edf b\u00e1n k\u1ebft v\u1edbi U23 Qatar.<br>\r\n<span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;\nline-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/chuyen-gia-noi-gi-khi-cong-phuong-hai-lan-da-hong-phat-den-168-194501.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/14/congphuongdl_ynhd.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/chuyen-gia-noi-gi-khi-cong-phuong-hai-lan-da-hong-phat-den-168-194501.html\">C\u00e1c chuy\u00ean gia n\u00f3i g\u00ec khi C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng hai l\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e1 h\u1ecfng ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n?</span><br>\r\nCh\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn vi\u1ec7c ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng hai l\u1ea7n th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n kh\u00f4ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u00e1c qu\u1ea3 \u0111\u00e1 11m, c\u1ea3 chuy\u00ean gia b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Tr\u1ecbnh Minh Hu\u1ebf l\u1eabn BLV Quang Huy \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a ra...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/thay-gi-sau-tran-olympic-viet-nam-30-olympic-pakistan-168-194498.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/14/thay-gi-sau-tran-olympic-viet-nam-30-olympic-pakistan.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/thay-gi-sau-tran-olympic-viet-nam-30-olympic-pakistan-168-194498.html\">Th\u1ea5y g\u00ec sau tr\u1eadn Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam 3-0 Olympic Pakistan?</span><br>\r\n\u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u di\u1ec5n ra chi\u1ec1u 14/8, \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng kh\u00f4ng m\u1ea5y kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Olympic Pakistan. V\u00e0 d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n \u1edf...</div>\r\n</div>\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)</div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5493","checkdouble":"194504"},{"date":"23:17 14/08","title":"Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam thay \u0111\u1ed5i k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng Pakistan","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/14/olympic-viet-nam-thay-doi-ke-hoach-tap-luyen-sau-tran-thang-pakistan.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>V\u1edbi 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 3 sao tr\u01b0\u1edbc Pakistan \u1edf ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n ASIAD v\u00e0o chi\u1ec1u nay 14/8, \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 \u0111i\u1ec1u ch\u1ec9nh trong k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n.\r\n\r\n</h2><h2>Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam thay \u0111\u1ed5i k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam thay \u0111\u1ed5i k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng Pakis h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam thay \u0111\u1ed5i k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng Pakis h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/14/photo-9-15342012338401446270955.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd t\u00e2p v\u00e0o bu\u1ed5i s\u00e1ng thay v\u00ec c\u00e1c bu\u1ed5i chi\u1ec1u nh\u01b0 th\u01b0\u1eddng l\u1ec7</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 3-0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Olympic Pakistan, HLV Park Hang Seo \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh thay \u0111\u1ed5i l\u1ecbch t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam\u00a0t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, theo Tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111o\u00e0n D\u01b0\u01a1ng V\u0169 L\u00e2m, s\u00e1ng mai (15/8), Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd c\u00f3 bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp nh\u1eb9 l\u00fac 10h30. To\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 y\u1ebfu s\u1ebd t\u1eadp nh\u1eb9 \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00fap c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 duy tr\u00ec c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c b\u00f3ng v\u00e0 nhanh ch\u00f3ng h\u1ed3i ph\u1ee5c th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Pakistan.</p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ea1i bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y mai, \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u0169ng s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i m\u1ed9t s\u00e2n b\u00f3ng m\u1edbi, c\u00e1ch kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 xa kh\u00e1ch s\u1ea1n n\u01a1i \u0111\u00f3ng qu\u00e2n, thay v\u00ec ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c t\u1eadp t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a nh\u00e0 m\u00e1y Samsung hay di chuy\u1ec3n g\u1ea7n 50 km t\u1edbi s\u00e2n t\u1eadp do Ban t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c b\u1ed1 tr\u00ed.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd gi\u00fap c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ecba \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt cho c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u s\u1eafp t\u1edbi t\u1ea1i ASIAD. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, do s\u00e2n b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a nh\u00e0 m\u00e1y Samsung kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n n\u00ean to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i luy\u1ec7n t\u1eadp trong s\u00e2n c\u1ecf nh\u00e2n t\u1ea1o.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ed1 tr\u00ed s\u00e2n m\u1edbi th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo s\u1ebd y\u00ean t\u00e2m h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ec3 ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t hai tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i \u1edf b\u1ea3ng D g\u1eb7p Nepal v\u00e0 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n. L\u00fac n\u00e0y \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111ang x\u1ebfp tr\u00ean Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng/b\u1ea1i. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u1ebfu ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y tr\u01b0\u1edbc Nepal, ch\u00fang ta ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 x\u1ebfp tr\u00ean Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n sau l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i n\u1ebfu c\u1ea7m h\u00f2a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y c\u0169ng gi\u00fap \u0111o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n \u00e1o \u0111\u1ecf tr\u00e1nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c vi\u1ec7c ph\u1ea3i g\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u1ea5t b\u1ea3ng E t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u knock-out, nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd l\u00e0 \u0110T Olympic H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/chuyen-gia-noi-gi-khi-cong-phuong-hai-lan-da-hong-phat-den-168-194501.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/14/congphuongdl_ynhd.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/chuyen-gia-noi-gi-khi-cong-phuong-hai-lan-da-hong-phat-den-168-194501.html\">C\u00e1c chuy\u00ean gia n\u00f3i g\u00ec khi C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng hai l\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e1 h\u1ecfng ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n?</span><br>\r\nCh\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn vi\u1ec7c ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng hai l\u1ea7n th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n kh\u00f4ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u00e1c qu\u1ea3 \u0111\u00e1 11m, c\u1ea3 chuy\u00ean gia b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Tr\u1ecbnh Minh Hu\u1ebf l\u1eabn BLV Quang Huy \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a ra...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-park-hang-seo-van-chua-hai-long-du-thang-pakistan-168-194496.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/14/hlv-park-hang-seo-van-chua-hai-long-du-thang-pakistan.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-park-hang-seo-van-chua-hai-long-du-thang-pakistan-168-194496.html\">HLV Park Hang Seo v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng d\u00f9 th\u1eafng Pakistan</span><br>\r\nSau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, HLV Park Hang Seo \u0111\u00e3 cho bi\u1ebft \u00f4ng kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1ec1 m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 d\u00f9 Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 3-0.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;\nline-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5492","checkdouble":"194505"},{"date":"18:25 14/08","title":"Klopp: \u201cDeschamps khi\u1ebfn \u0110T Ph\u00e1p tr\u1edf n\u00ean nh\u00e0m ch\u00e1n\u201d","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/16/jurgen-klopp-phat-bieu-ve-didier-deschamps.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Jurgen Klopp ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Didier Deschamps. Chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c ca ng\u1ee3i \u0111\u1ed3ng nghi\u1ec7p \u0111\u01b0a \u0110T Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u1ebfn ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018 d\u00f9 th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn \u0111\u00f4i l\u00fac xem h\u1ecd thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00e1 nh\u00e0m ch\u00e1n.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Ph\u00e1p gi\u00e0nh ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nT\u1ea1i World Cup 2018, \u0110T Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch. Sau tr\u00f2n 20 n\u0103m, Les Bleus l\u1ea1i c\u00f3 th\u00eam m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n l\u00ean \u0111\u1ec9nh th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi. Didier Deschamps l\u00e0 nh\u00e2n ch\u1ee9ng s\u1ed1ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea3 hai chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111\u00f3. \u00d4ng l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng Ph\u00e1p n\u00e2ng cao c\u00fap v\u00e0ng tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 n\u0103m 1998 tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi d\u1eabn d\u1eaft h\u1ecd \u0111\u0103ng quang t\u1ea1i n\u01b0\u1edbc Nga.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ede chung k\u1ebft, Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Croatia 4-2 b\u1edfi c\u00e1c b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Antoine Griezmann, Paul Pogba v\u00e0 Kylian Mbappe c\u00f9ng 1 pha ph\u1ea3n l\u01b0\u1edbi c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng. Chung k\u1ebft c\u1ed9ng v\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 4-3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Argentina t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 1/8 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 2 tr\u1eadn t\u01b0ng b\u1eebng nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 l\u1ee5c lam t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Jurgen Klopp ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Didier Deschamps h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Jurgen Klopp ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Didier Deschamps h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/16/jurgen-klopp-phat-bieu-ve-didier-deschamps.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Jurgen Klopp ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Didier Deschamps</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Klopp nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t v\u1ec1 Deschamps</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, xuy\u00ean su\u1ed1t World Cup 2018, \u0110T Ph\u00e1p cho kh\u00e1n gi\u1ea3 th\u1ea5y m\u1ed9t phong c\u00e1ch th\u1ef1c d\u1ee5ng l\u00e0 ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ea1o. H\u1ecd th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean l\u00f9i s\u00e2u ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 ch\u1edd ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng sau khi \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 b\u00e0n d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc. Ch\u00ednh Jurgen Klopp ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Didier Deschamps c\u0169ng kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Ph\u00e1p.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cPh\u00e1p \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0 m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt \u0111\u00fang \u0111\u1eafn\u201d, HLV c\u1ee7a Liverpool n\u00f3i trong m\u1ed9t cu\u1ed9c ph\u1ecfng v\u1ea5n v\u1edbi France Football. \u201cDidier Deschamps c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a ra nh\u1eefng quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00e1c v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y. H\u00e3y \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1ecd ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng, ch\u1ea1y, k\u00edch th\u00edch c\u1ea3 th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi v\u1edbi l\u1ed1i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 \u0111\u1eb9p c\u1ee7a Ph\u00e1p.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cNh\u01b0ng Deschamps \u0111\u00e3 cho th\u1ea5y s\u1ef1 th\u0103ng ti\u1ebfn \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3. \u00d4ng \u1ea5y bi\u1ebft l\u00e0m d\u1ecbu v\u00e0 c\u0169ng x\u1eed l\u00fd k\u1ef7 lu\u1eadt h\u1ee3p l\u00fd. Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed, \u0111\u00f4i l\u00fac c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd tr\u1edf n\u00ean nh\u00e0m ch\u00e1n. C\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t HLV l\u00e0 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng nh\u1eefng ph\u1ea9m ch\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\nPh\u00e1p s\u1ebd c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean sau ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi l\u00e0 g\u1eb7p \u0110\u1ee9c tr\u00ean s\u00e2n kh\u00e1ch trong tr\u1eadn m\u1edf m\u00e0n UEFA Nations League v\u00e0o \u0111\u00eam 8/9 t\u1edbi. Kh\u00f4ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng nh\u01b0 Ph\u00e1p, \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 s\u1eafp t\u1edbi c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd thi \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng v\u00e0 d\u1eebng ch\u00e2n ngay v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng.<br>\r\n<strong><br>\r\nXem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 \u0110T Ph\u00e1p tr\u00ean trang bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/sao-man-city-ghen-ti-voi-nhung-nha-vo-dich-the-gioi-172-191812.html\">Sao Man City ghen t\u1ecb v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-phap/bakayoko-mbappe-la-cau-thu-tot-nhat-the-gioi-197-191747.html\">Kylian Mbappe l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/doi-truong-phap-tiet-lo-dieu-dac-biet-sau-chien-thang-truoc-argentina-421-191641.html\">\u0110\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng Ph\u00e1p ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Argentina</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/sep-dt-phap-boc-tran-su-that-kho-tin-ve-zidane-421-191628.html\">S\u1ebfp \u0110T Ph\u00e1p b\u00f3c tr\u1ea7n s\u1ef1 th\u1eadt kh\u00f3 tin v\u1ec1 Zidane</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/hlv-deschamps-phat-bieu-ve-dt-phap-sau-world-cup-2018-421-191613.html\">Deschamps quy\u1ebft kh\u00f4ng nh\u01b0\u1eddng gh\u1ebf HLV Ph\u00e1p cho Zidane</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5491","checkdouble":"194483"},{"date":"20:48 14/08","title":"Sao s\u00e1ng Croatia gi\u00e3 t\u1eeb s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/14/mario-mandzukic-chia-tay-dt-croatia.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Mario Mandzukic chia tay \u0110T Croatia. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ed3ng ngh\u0129a v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i 2-4 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p t\u1ea1i chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 l\u00e0 l\u1ea7n cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o n\u00e0y kho\u00e1c l\u00ean m\u00ecnh chi\u1ebfc \u00e1o caro.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2><br>\r\nMandzukic c\u00f9ng Croatia l\u00e0m n\u00ean k\u1ef3 t\u00edch</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110T Croatia \u0111\u00e3 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc \u0111\u1ee9ng \u0111\u1ea7u v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng d\u00f9 r\u01a1i v\u00e0o b\u1ea3ng t\u1eed th\u1ea7n v\u1edbi Argentina, Nigeria v\u00e0 Iceland. H\u1ecd to\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ea3 3 tr\u1eadn v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng, bao g\u1ed3m c\u1ea3 m\u00e0n h\u1ea1 b\u1ec7 Argentina 3 b\u00e0n kh\u00f4ng g\u1ee1.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nCroatia c\u1ee9 th\u1ebf ti\u1ebfn t\u1eebng b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u1eefng ch\u1eafc, v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua \u0110an M\u1ea1ch, ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Nga r\u1ed3i Anh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111i t\u1edbi chung k\u1ebft v\u1edbi Ph\u00e1p. \u1ede tr\u1eadn cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng, h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m g\u00ec kh\u00e1c ngo\u00e0i th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p s\u1edf h\u1eefu d\u00e0n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Mario Mandzukic chia tay \u0110T Croatia h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Mario Mandzukic chia tay \u0110T Croatia h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/16/Mario-Mandzukic-chia-tay-DT-Croatia-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">V\u00e0o chung k\u1ebft World Cup l\u00e0 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng l\u1edbn c\u1ee7a Croatia</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ede chung k\u1ebft, Mario Mandzukic \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng sai l\u1ea7m c\u1ee7a th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Hugo Lloris b\u00ean ph\u00eda Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u1ec3 ghi 1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng. Trong to\u00e0n b\u1ed9 gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u, ch\u00e2n s\u00fat 32 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 3 pha l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng (tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi \u0110an M\u1ea1ch v\u00e0 Anh).<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Chia tay \u0110TQG</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, th\u00f4ng tin Mario Mandzukic chia tay \u0110T Croatia \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u00ednh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn qua trang c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n. \u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed3ng ngh\u0129a v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 l\u00e0 l\u1ea7n cu\u1ed1i anh kho\u00e1c l\u00ean m\u00ecnh chi\u1ebfc \u00e1o caro.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"tien dao Mario Mandzukic\" title=\"tien dao Mario Mandzukic\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/14/mario-mandzukic-chia-tay-dt-croatia.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Mario Mandzukic chia tay \u0110T Croatia</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cHuy ch\u01b0\u01a1ng b\u1ea1c World Cup \u0111\u00e3 cho t\u00f4i n\u0103ng l\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u1edbi, nh\u01b0ng n\u00f3 c\u0169ng khi\u1ebfn cho quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n n\u00e0y d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng h\u01a1n m\u1ed9t ch\u00fat\u201d, Mandzukic vi\u1ebft. \u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 bi\u1ebfn \u01b0\u1edbc m\u01a1 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh th\u00e0nh s\u1ef1 th\u1eadt, \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng l\u1ecbch s\u1eed v\u00e0 tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m s\u1ef1 \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 tin n\u1ed5i t\u1eeb ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cTh\u1eddi gian qua, bao g\u1ed3m s\u1ef1 ch\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3n t\u1ea1i qu\u00ea nh\u00e0, s\u1ebd l\u00e0 k\u1ef7 ni\u1ec7m \u0111\u00e1ng nh\u1edb nh\u1ea5t trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ee3t t\u1eadp trung \u0110TQG v\u00e0 tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 qu\u00ea h\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1eb9p nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i. T\u00f4i h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac, m\u00e3n nguy\u1ec7n v\u00e0 v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o v\u1ec1 t\u1ea5m huy ch\u01b0\u01a1ng b\u1ea1c World Cup.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trui r\u00e8n qua nhi\u1ec1u n\u0103m, qua n\u1ed7i \u0111au, n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c, s\u1ef1 t\u1eebng tr\u1ea3i, th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng v\u00e0 nh\u1eefng kho\u1ea3nh kh\u1eafc kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n. Kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m l\u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e3 t\u1eeb s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf. N\u1ebfu c\u00f3 th\u1ec3, t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd ch\u01a1i cho Croatia cho \u0111\u1ebfn khi ch\u1ebft b\u1edfi \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o v\u00f4 h\u1ea1n.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cNh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y ng\u00e0y \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ebfn v\u1edbi t\u00f4i, ngay l\u00fac n\u00e0y. T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 c\u1ed1ng hi\u1ebfn h\u1ebft m\u00ecnh cho Croatia, t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p v\u00e0o th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Croatia t\u1eeb tr\u01b0\u1edbc t\u1edbi nay.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u1ef1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a Bayern Munich v\u00e0 Atletico Madrid c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 Croatia. Anh n\u00f3i th\u00eam:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cKh\u00f4ng ai ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o. T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i, m\u1ea5t b\u00f3ng v\u00e0 chuy\u1ec1n h\u1ecfng. Tuy nhi\u00ean, t\u00f4i lu\u00f4n c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng h\u1ebft m\u00ecnh, thi \u0111\u1ea5u h\u1ebft kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. C\u1ea3m \u01a1n v\u00ec m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eadn ra \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y, s\u00e1t c\u00e1nh c\u00f9ng t\u00f4i v\u00e0 Croatia. T\u1eeb h\u00f4m nay, v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i l\u00e0 b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n, nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 Croatia trung th\u00e0nh nh\u1ea5t.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 \u0110T Croatia tr\u00ean trang bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/tao-ky-tich-o-world-cup-hlv-croatia-tu-lam-gia-ban-than-184-191815.html\">T\u1ea1o k\u1ef3 t\u00edch \u1edf World Cup, HLV Croatia t\u1ef1 l\u00e0m gi\u00e1 b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/bai-hoc-tu-nguoi-croatia-dat-nuoc-nho-giac-mo-lon-421-191456.html\">B\u00e0i h\u1ecdc t\u1eeb ng\u01b0\u1eddi Croatia: \u0110\u1ea5t n\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u1ecf, gi\u1ea5c m\u01a1 l\u1edbn</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nghi-van-hcv-world-cup-2018-bi-danh-cap-421-191442.html\">Nghi v\u1ea5n: Huy ch\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00e0ng World Cup 2018 b\u1ecb \u0111\u00e1nh c\u1eafp?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/croatia-tai-world-cup-2018-ngay-mai-bat-dau-tu-hom-nay-421-191422.html\">Croatia h\u1eadu World Cup 2018: Ng\u00e0y mai b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1eeb h\u00f4m nay</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/dt-croatia-ve-nuoc-duoc-ho-tong-bang-may-bay-chien-dau-465-191383.html\">\u0110T Croatia \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ed9 t\u1ed1ng b\u1eb1ng m\u00e1y bay chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u trong ng\u00e0y tr\u1edf v\u1ec1</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5490","checkdouble":"194497"},{"date":"22:23 14/08","title":"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ed1i 14/8: M.U b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd mu\u1ed1n chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Leroy Sane \u201cphi\u00ean b\u1ea3n 2.0\u201d","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/14/diem-tin-bong-da-toi-148-mu-bat-ngo-muon-chieu-mo-leroy-sane-phien-ban-20.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>M.U mu\u1ed1n \u201csao mai\u201d Bundesliga, Real t\u00ednh mua h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Chelsea, PSG s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng tr\u1ea3 100 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho Eriksen,\u2026 l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c c\u00f3 trong \u0111i\u1ec3m tin t\u1ed1i 14/8.</h2><h2>M.U nh\u1eafm \u201csao mai\u201d Bundesliga</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo b\u00e1o gi\u1edbi Anh, CLB Man United \u0111ang \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1eaft t\u1edbi sao tr\u1ebb Linton Maina, t\u00e0i n\u0103ng thu\u1ed9c bi\u00ean ch\u1ebf Hannover 96. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 thu h\u00fat s\u1ef1 ch\u00fa \u00fd c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c tuy\u1ec3n tr\u1ea1ch vi\u00ean Man Utd sau nh\u1eefng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u1edf giai \u0111o\u1ea1n ti\u1ec1n m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i, theo Sportbuzzer. Tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 U-19 \u0110\u1ee9c c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u00ec v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t Leroy Sane m\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ed1i 148 MU mu\u1ed1n chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 sao tr\u1ebb Bundesliga h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ed1i 148 MU mu\u1ed1n chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 sao tr\u1ebb Bundesliga h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/14/linton-maina-1.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>M.U b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd mu\u1ed1n chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Linton Maina (tr\u00e1i)</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Real mu\u1ed1n mua h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Chelsea<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo t\u1edd Don Balon, CLB Real Madrid s\u1ebd ch\u1ecdn Marcos Alonso c\u1ee7a Chelsea l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau thay th\u1ebf cho Marcelo trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y r\u1eddi Bernabeu \u0111\u1ea7u qu\u00e2n cho Juventus<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">2 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 tr\u00e1i ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha ch\u01a1i c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Chelsea. Kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 ph\u00f2ng th\u1ee7 hay, Alonso c\u00f2n c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng. Real \u0111ang hy v\u1ecdng s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n 45 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London nh\u1ea3 ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>Man Utd t\u1ef1 tin gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n De Gea</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1edd BBC\u00a0ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9, \"Qu\u1ef7 \u0110\u1ecf\" r\u1ea5t t\u1ef1 tin v\u00e0o vi\u1ec7c gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n David De Gea, nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 sau khi Real Madrid c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Thibaut Courtois t\u1eeb Chelsea. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 l\u00fd do gi\u1ea3i th\u00edch vi\u1ec7c th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1ed9t n\u0103m v\u1edbi Man Utd nh\u01b0ng l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o s\u00e2n Old Trafford kh\u00f4ng v\u1ed9i v\u00e0ng trong chuy\u1ec7n gia h\u1ea1n.\u00a0<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>PSG g\u1eedi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb 100 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng h\u1ecfi mua Eriksen<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng Anh \u0111\u01b0a tin PSG \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eedi l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb 100 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng h\u1ecfi mua Christian Eriksen t\u1eeb Tottenham. \u0110\u00e2y la\u0300 \u0111\u00f4\u0323ng tha\u0301i kh\u00f4ng qua\u0301 b\u00e2\u0301t ng\u01a1\u0300 trong b\u00f4\u0301i ca\u0309nh Adrien Rabiot \u0111a\u0301nh ti\u00ea\u0301ng mu\u00f4\u0301n r\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4 n\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">H\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a Eriksen v\u1edbi Tottenham ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n t\u1edbi H\u00e8 2020. B\u1edfi v\u1eady, \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m th\u00edch h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ec3 PSH h\u1ecfi mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>\u0110\u1ed3ng h\u01b0\u01a1ng Salah mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Arsenal<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ai C\u1eadp \u0111ang mong mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 chia tay Arsenal khi anh kh\u00f4ng n\u1eb1m trong k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch c\u1ee7a Unai Emery, sau s\u1ef1 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i\u00a0Lucas Torreira v\u00e0 Mateo Guendouzi.\u00a0Mohamed Elneny mu\u1ed1n ra \u0111i trong h\u00e8 n\u00e0y d\u00f9 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y m\u1edbi gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u1ed3i th\u00e1ng 3 v\u1eeba qua.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>Milan mua sao x\u1ecbt c\u1ee7a Chelsea</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u1ea3 hai CLB c\u1ee7a Anh v\u00e0 Italy \u0111\u1ed3ng lo\u1ea1t x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn v\u1ee5 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Tiemoue Bakayoko. AC Milan s\u1ebd m\u01b0\u1ee3n ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p trong m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a, k\u00e8m \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n mua \u0111\u1ee9t tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 40 tri\u1ec7u \u0111\u00f4la.\u00a0C\u1ef1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Monaco l\u00e0 t\u00e2n binh th\u1ee9 s\u00e1u c\u1ee7a Milan m\u00f9a n\u00e0y, sau Pepe Reina, Ivan Strinic, Mattia Caldara, Samu Castillejo, v\u00e0 Gonzalo Higuain.</p>\r\n<h2>Herrera b\u00f3ng gi\u00f3 ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Ander Herrerra d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 mu\u1ed1n kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh anh s\u1ebd gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Man Utd. \"Tr\u01b0\u1edbc h\u1ebft, t\u00f4i c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o khi t\u00f4i ch\u01a1i cho Manchester United. T\u00f4i t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o v\u00ec \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ch\u01a1i cho CLB. T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 HLV r\u1ea5t h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi t\u00f4i, C\u0110V n\u01a1i \u0111\u00e2y c\u0169ng \u0111ang h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi t\u00f4i, \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 khi\u1ebfn t\u00f4i th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 r\u1ea5t vui.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u00f4i lu\u00f4n ghi nh\u1edb t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u, nh\u1eefng k\u1ef7 ni\u1ec7m v\u1edbi CLB. T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u danh hi\u1ec7u , t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i h\u01a1n 160 tr\u1eadn cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng. V\u00e0 trong t\u00e2m tr\u00ed t\u00f4i lu\u00f4n ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng t\u00f4i s\u1ebd ch\u01a1i h\u01a1n 200 tr\u1eadn v\u00e0 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c c\u1ed1ng hi\u1ebfn b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n cho CLB\".</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">XEM TH\u00caM:\u00a0<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-chau-au/diem-tin-bong-da-sang-ngay-148-mu-sap-hoan-tat-ban-hop-dong-trong-mo-184-194435.html\" target=\"_blank\">\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y 14/8: M.U s\u1eafp ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng trong m\u01a1<br>\r\n<br type=\"_moz\">\r\n</span></div>\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)</div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5489","checkdouble":"194502"},{"date":"06:31 15/08","title":"L\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1 v\u00f2ng s\u01a1 lo\u1ea1i th\u1ee9 3 Champions League 2018/19: Nhi\u1ec1u t\u00ean tu\u1ed5i ng\u00e3 ng\u1ef1a","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/15/luot-ve-vong-so-loai-thu-3-champions-league-201819-nhieu-ten-tuoi-nga-ngua.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>V\u00f2ng s\u01a1 lo\u1ea1i th\u1ee9 3 Champions League 2018/19 ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn s\u1ef1 ng\u00e3 ng\u1ef1a c\u1ee7a h\u00e0ng lo\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng t\u00ean tu\u1ed5i nh\u01b0 Celtic, Fenerbahce hay Spartak Moscow.</h2><div style=\"text-align: left;\">\u0110\u1ec3 cho AEK Athens c\u1ea7m ch\u00e2n 1-1 \u1edf tr\u1eadn l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1m x\u1ea5u d\u00e0nh cho Celtic. V\u00e0 qu\u1ea3 th\u1ef1c, g\u00e3 kh\u1ed5ng l\u1ed3 c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Scotland \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i tr\u1ea3 gi\u00e1 cho vi\u1ec7c kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf s\u00e2n b\u00e3i. \u1ede tr\u1eadn l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1, AEK Athens nhanh ch\u00f3ng \u00e1p \u0111\u1eb7t th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn v\u00e0 ghi li\u1ec1n 2 b\u00e0n v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi Celtic \u1edf c\u00e1c ph\u00fat 6 v\u00e0 50. Celtic ch\u1ed1ng \u0111\u1ee1 ch\u1eadt v\u1eadt v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e0n g\u1ee1 danh d\u1ef1 \u1edf ph\u00fat 78 do c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Scott Sinclair.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/15/celtic.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u00a0</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u1eadn k\u1ebft c\u1ee5c t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 Celtic l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Th\u1ed5 Nh\u0129 K\u1ef3 Fenerbahce. Ch\u1ec9 kh\u00e1c l\u00e0 Fenerbahce \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1eadn l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Benfica v\u00e0 th\u00fac th\u1ee7 0-1. \u0110\u1ebfn tr\u1eadn l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1, h\u1ecd nh\u1eadn g\u00e1o n\u01b0\u1edbc l\u1ea1nh ngay trong hi\u1ec7p 1 khi Gedson Fernandes m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 cho \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00e1ch. V\u1edbi b\u00e0n thua n\u00e0y, Fenerbahce c\u1ea7n ghi 3 b\u00e0n \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp v\u00e0 h\u1ecd ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 1/3 con s\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ec1 ra.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1ed9t t\u00ean tu\u1ed5i l\u1edbn kh\u00e1c c\u0169ng ph\u1ea3i d\u1eebng chuy\u1ebfn phi\u00eau l\u01b0u \u1edf v\u00f2ng s\u01a1 lo\u1ea1i th\u1ee9 ba Champions League l\u00e0 Spartak Moscow. \u0110\u1ec3 thua PAOK Thessaloniki 2-3 tr\u00ean s\u00e2n \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i, nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc Nga ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 ghi 1 b\u00e0n \u1edf tr\u1eadn l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp. Th\u1ebf nh\u01b0ng, su\u1ed1t 90 ph\u00fat, h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n ch\u1ecdc th\u1ee7ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u00e0nh l\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Hy L\u1ea1p v\u00e0 b\u1ea5t l\u1ef1c b\u1ecb c\u1ea7m h\u00f2a 0-0 ngay tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ede nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00e1c, h\u1ea7u h\u1ebft \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao h\u01a1n, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f3 t\u00ean tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u1ec1u gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng t\u01b0ng b\u1eebng. \u0110i\u1ec3n h\u00ecnh l\u00e0 Dinamo Kiev, Dinamo Zagreb hay Ajax Amsterdam. Chi\u1ec1u t\u1ed1i nay, s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra l\u1ec5 b\u1ed1c th\u0103m chia c\u1eb7p v\u00f2ng play-off Champions League 2018/19.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nK\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 c\u1ee5 th\u1ec3<br>\r\n<br>\r\nDinamo Kiev 2-0 Slavia Prague (t\u1ed5ng t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 3-1)<br>\r\nBATE Borisov 1-1 Qarabag FK (2-1)<br>\r\nSpartak Moscow 0-0 PAOK Thessaloniki FC (2-3)<br>\r\nAEK Athens 2-1 Celtic (3-2)<br>\r\nDinamo Zagreb 1-0 FC Astana (3-0)<br>\r\nFenerbahce 1-1 Benfica (1-2)<br>\r\nVidi FC 0-0 Malmoe FF (1-1)<br>\r\nKF Shkendija 0-1 Salzburg (0-4)<br>\r\nAjax 3-0 Standard Liege (5-2)<br>\r\nSpartak Trnava 1-2 FK Crvena Zvezda (2-3)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5488","checkdouble":"194509"},{"date":"18:08 14/08","title":"Ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n b\u00e1o tin bu\u1ed3n cho Real v\u1ee5 Modric","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/18/nguoi-dai-dien-bao-tin-buon-cho-real-vu-modric.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Marko Naletilic ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Luka Modric, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 33 tu\u1ed5i kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh th\u00e2n ch\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh mu\u1ed1n t\u1edbi Inter Milan.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Modric b\u1ecb \u0111\u1eb7t nhi\u1ec1u d\u1ea5u h\u1ecfi</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nT\u1ea1i World Cup 2018, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Luka Modric \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t. Nh\u1eefng \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p c\u1ee7a anh gi\u00fap Croatia l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ebfn tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1985 c\u0169ng nh\u1eadn danh hi\u1ec7u C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u.\u00a0<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Marko Naletilic ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Luka Modric h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Marko Naletilic ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Luka Modric h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/7/Marko-Naletilic-phat-bieu-ve-Luka-Modric-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Luka Modric \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Inter Milan theo \u0111u\u1ed5i</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong nh\u1eefng m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Croatia c\u0169ng ch\u01a1i c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t, anh duy tr\u00ec phong \u0111\u1ed9 r\u1ea5t \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh. Modric l\u00e0 tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t n\u01a1i tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa c\u1ee7a Real Madrid, anh c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi Toni Kroos l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m hay nh\u1ea5t ch\u00e2u \u00c2u.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 33 tu\u1ed5i nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m t\u1eeb nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn. Liverpool, Chelsea, PSG, Juventus \u0111\u1ec1u mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Croatia, song Inter Milan \u0111ang l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng kh\u00e1t khao c\u1ef1u sao Tottenham nh\u1ea5t.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 ngu\u1ed3n tin \u1edf Italia c\u00f2n kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Modric mu\u1ed1n t\u1edbi Inter Milan thi \u0111\u1ea5u, anh s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng ra \u0111i n\u1ebfu nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb h\u1ee3p l\u00fd. <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-italia/inter-quyet-tam-chieu-mo-bang-duoc-luka-modric-176-193748.html\" target=\"_blank\">Inter mu\u1ed1n mua Modric</span>, h\u1ecd ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 45 tri\u1ec7u euro cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn Modric mu\u1ed1n t\u1edbi Inter Milan</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Marko Naletilic ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Luka Modric, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 33 tu\u1ed5i kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh th\u00e2n ch\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh mu\u1ed1n t\u1edbi Inter Milan.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Luka Modric den Inter\" title=\"Luka Modric den Inter\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/7/luka-modric-tinh-roi-real-sang-inter-milan.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn Luka Modric mu\u1ed1n t\u1edbi Inter Milan</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n\u201cModric \u0111ang ngh\u0129 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ebfn Inter, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111ang ngh\u0129 \u0111\u1ebfn vi\u1ec7c tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh trung t\u00e2m trong l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Italia. T\u00f4i c\u00f3 c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c s\u1edbm hay mu\u1ed9n, Modric s\u1ebd ch\u01a1i \u1edf Italia. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y y\u00eau th\u00edch m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 \u1edf Serie A, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y mu\u1ed1n thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf \u0111\u00e2y\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec Marko Naletilic ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u, r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng Modric \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n t\u1edbi Inter Milan. V\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Italia l\u00e0 h\u1ecd c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c Real b\u00e1n ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh hay kh\u00f4ng m\u00e0 th\u00f4i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nModric \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 257 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n cho Real Madrid, ghi 13 b\u00e0n. Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Perez c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Madrid kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh ch\u1ec9 b\u00e1n ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Croatia n\u1ebfu nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 750 tri\u1ec7u euro.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5487","checkdouble":"194480"},{"date":"06:26 15/08","title":"HLV Lopetegui mu\u1ed1n n\u1ed5 bom t\u1ea5n, BL\u0110 Real n\u00f3i kh\u00f4ng","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/15/hlv-lopetegui-muon-no-bom-tan-bld-real-noi-khong.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>T\u00e2n HLV Julen Lopetegui mu\u1ed1n mua th\u00eam m\u1ed9t trung v\u1ec7 v\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trung phong, nh\u01b0ng Real ch\u1ec9 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 ph\u1ea3i ch\u0103ng.</h2><div style=\"text-align: left;\">Theo t\u1edd AS, Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Florentino Perez hi\u1ec7n ch\u01b0a mu\u1ed1n chi qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u ti\u1ec1n cho m\u1ed9t v\u00e0i c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 nh\u01b0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc. Ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ee9ng \u0111\u1ea7u Real cho r\u1eb1ng th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111ang tr\u1edf n\u00ean ''\u0111i\u00ean r\u1ed3'' sau v\u1ee5 PSG mua Neymar n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i v\u00e0 Chelsea mua th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Kepa n\u0103m nay. \u0110\u00e2y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn \u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb mua m\u1edbi m\u1ed9t trung v\u1ec7 v\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o c\u1ee7a HLV Lopetegui.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Lopetegui mu\u1ed1n n\u1ed5 bom t\u1ea5n, BL\u0110 Real n\u00f3i kh\u00f4ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Lopetegui mu\u1ed1n n\u1ed5 bom t\u1ea5n, BL\u0110 Real n\u00f3i kh\u00f4ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/15/lo2-4997-1534216722.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Lopetegui b\u1ecb bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i d\u00f9ng s\u1ed1 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 hi\u1ec7n c\u00f3, tr\u1eeb khi Real mua \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u00eam v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 cao. \u1ea2nh: Reuters</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNgo\u00e0i ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o tr\u1ebb Vinicius v\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c mua t\u1eeb k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc, Real m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 th\u00eam m\u1ed9t t\u00e2n binh trong h\u00e8 n\u0103m nay l\u00e0 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Thibaut Courtois. S\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n m\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng kim v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch ch\u00e2u \u00c2u b\u1ecf ra \u0111\u1ec3 mua Courtois ch\u1ec9 kho\u1ea3ng 40 tri\u1ec7u \u0111\u00f4la, ch\u01b0a b\u1eb1ng m\u1ed9t n\u1eeda so v\u1edbi Kepa.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTrung phong v\u1ed1n l\u00e0 v\u1ecb tr\u00ed m\u00e0 Rea kh\u00f3 b\u1ed5 sung nh\u1ea5t trong hai m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i qua. Trong khi Karim Benzema c\u00f3 d\u1ea5u hi\u1ec7u xu\u1ed1ng s\u1ee9c, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn kh\u00e1c l\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o tr\u1ebb Borja Mayoral. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nVi\u1ec7c t\u00ecm ng\u01b0\u1eddi t\u1eeb b\u00ean ngo\u00e0i c\u0169ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n v\u1edbi Real. Bayern ch\u01b0a ch\u1ecbu nh\u1ea3 Robert Lewandowski, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed h\u00e9t gi\u00e1 h\u00e0ng tr\u0103m tri\u1ec7u \u0111\u00f4la.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nHLV Lopetegui c\u0169ng c\u00f3 l\u00fd do \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a ra y\u00eau c\u1ea7u b\u1ed5 sung th\u00eam m\u1ed9t trung v\u1ec7. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb Jesus Vallejo hi\u1ec7n ch\u01b0a \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c y\u00eau c\u1ea7u thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ec9nh cao, trong khi Sergio Ramos, Raphael Varane v\u00e0 Nacho c\u1ea7n c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb n\u1ebfu g\u1eb7p ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTheo t\u1edd AS, v\u1edbi ch\u00ednh s\u00e1ch ti\u1ebft ki\u1ec7m, Real \u0111ang chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n l\u1edbn \u0111\u1ec3 mua Neymar. Kylian Mbappe c\u0169ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau m\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng kim v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch ch\u00e2u \u00c2u d\u1ef1 t\u00ednh s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i l\u1eadp m\u1ed9t k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u1edbi \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 mang v\u1ec1.</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5486","checkdouble":"194507"}]}